It's understood traffic is being diverted from Madiba Street to Lilian Ngoyi on Thursday morning. JOHANNESBURG - There are reports of taxi violence in the Pretoria CBD. It's understood traffic is being diverted from Madiba Street to Lilian Ngoyi on Thursday morning. This motorist says taxi drivers are fighting. “The situation is just too bad, even the innocent bystanders are being beaten up by possibly fighting taxi guys. People are shooting each other here, apparently, it’s taxis waging war against each other.”   